Name
	nginx-hashdos-patch
	This is a patch fixed the #hashDos# bug.

Version
	This document describes nginx-hashdos-patch v1.0 release on 1/3/2011.

Description
	Many more web platforms vulnerable to the hash collision attack.Nginx is the frontend.Nginx checking it and return a 413 header,when the hacker is posting the attacking data.

HowToInstall
	1.cd nginx-src/
	2.patch -p1 < nginx-hashdos-1.0.9.patch
	3.make && make install

Author
	54chen(czhttp@gmail.com)
	http://54chen.com

